text: Place is pretty old school style infrastructure. But residents can get all the basic needs for their family, even got furniture shops to visit if you need a new dining table or bed. The best is the food centre where there are plenty of good selection. Nearby also got MacDonald, turf soccer court and park as well to be even more complete.
Nice place to look for some good food during lunchtime.
Vast variety of food stalls. Prices are reasonable. People are friendly.
lots of good quality food options and wet market with easy parking
